{"id": "1504239656089161900", "channel_id": "1503356878804226169", "type": 19, "author_id": "188019082447028224", "author_name": "rileybou", "author_bot": false, "content": "Likely a variety of reasons, Saya no Uta was one of the first Lovecraftian horror video games and one of the biggest influences on horror anime in the early 2000s. It also has an iconic antagonist they could easily implement and a comparable genre and art style to Morimens, so that's likely the main reason it was chosen. It's also an older IP so licensing was probably a lot easier than many other potential collabs. I could see Claymore or Elfen Lied being interesting future collabs.", "timestamp": "2026-05-13T21:51:21.433000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1160510535670968330"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Alva_goodjob", "emoji_id": "1468259169965707398", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1503356878804226169", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1503356878804226169", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Saya collab and future plan", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1361169005435420785", "1181168158678204497", "1361168893200044183", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1504253819914158210", "channel_id": "1502914367329538130", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "I suggested to the devs to make pdive like R99 battle where:\n\n1. You actually want to max out the map, and not just find the shortest path.\n\n2. The boss has something like 10 or 20 lives. You fight them and each life the boss gets stronger/harder.\n\nWhenever you die, you get your score. You dont have to beat the boss. Its all about how far you can go and how many lives you can make it through. Not how many turns it took to get there.\n\nThis way anyone that has built up any 1 strong team, has a chance to prove how far their team can go.\n\nIts not just gMurphy gimmick and beat turn 1.", "timestamp": "2026-05-13T22:47:38.352000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-13T22:48:35.292000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["299947644208414720"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1504033251432599552", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1502914367329538130", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位吐槽完了，现在吐槽深潜当下的分数计算机制有够烂的", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1361169005435420785"]}
